Derived role from PI on Proposal Log
Award Budget Administrator - the role grants permissions to manage any award budget at OSP level
Maintain Award Budget - the role grants permissions to modify and submit award budget at departmental level
Award Budget Aggregator - the role grants permissions to create and maintain award budget at department level
Award Budget Approver - the role grants permissions to edit and approve award budget
Award Budget Modifier - the role grants permissions to modify or view award budget at departmental level
Award Budget Viewer - the role grants permissions to view award budget at departmental level
